4242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">　　<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-break:break-all;\">后勤部</strong></p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color:#424242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">　　负责管理协会财务及其他物品以及活动实施。</p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color:#424242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"> </p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color:#424242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">　　<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-break:break-all;\">宣传部</strong></p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color:#424242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">　　负责协会宣传与宣传品制作。</p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color:#424242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"> </p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color:#424242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">　　<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-break:break-all;\">办公室</strong></p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color:#424242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">　　负责协会对外联系。</p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color:#424242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"> </p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color:#424242;font-family:����;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"> </p><p style=\"padding:0px;word-break:break-all;color: